name: Gabriella Houston

She carries values of honesty, friendship, and lifelong learning. Her interests are as varied as exploring technology, hiking, going on detox trips, cooking, and photography. ARecent graduate, this Agnostic describes her politics as Liberal. She is looking for a long-term relationship but is open to short-term ones, whilst in a strong belief of monogamy. Born an Aries and typified as an ENFJ, she keeps active and sometimes drinks, yet smoking, marijuana, or drugs aren't for her. Dog and fish owner this woman of Hispanic/Latino heritage doesn’t have or want children.
